data.eml:eml: A new species of endemic frog belonging to genus Nannophrys Günther, 1869 (Anura: Dicroglossinae) from Sri Lanka

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fernando, Samantha Suranjan, Wickramasingha, Mendis, Rodirigo, Roshan K. (2007): A new species of endemic frog belonging to genus Nannophrys Günther, 1869 (Anura: Dicroglossinae) from Sri Lanka. Zootaxa 1403: 55-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.175474
